            "extra_id": 0x44,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x0,
            "msg_string": "Here, this should be everything."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x2,
            "name_id": 0x2,
            "extra_id": 0x21,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0x1,
            "msg_string": "Uu, I didn't think you'd actually be able to make it all..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x2,
            "msg_string": "Huh?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x2,
            "name_id": 0x2,
            "extra_id": 0x23,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0x3,
            "msg_string": "Nothing... I got it, I know I promised. I'll sing like I said I would."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x17,
            "expr_id": 0x2,
            "msg_id": 0x4,
            "msg_string": "Okay! Do your best."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x2,
            "name_id": 0x2,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x5,
            "msg_string": "*Sigh*... You seem happy about it."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x18,
            "expr_id": 0x2,
            "msg_id": 0x6,
            "msg_string": "Because I don't get to hear you sing very often. Of course I'd be happy."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x19,
            "expr_id": 0x2,
            "msg_id": 0x7,
            "msg_string": "You're really good at singing, but you never let me listen."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x2,
            "name_id": 0x2,
            "extra_id": 0x21,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0x8,
            "msg_string": "Because it's embarrassing. I like singing, but not in front of other people..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x1,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x9,
            "msg_string": "You'll do fine, I know you will!"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x2,
            "name_id": 0x2,
            "extra_id": 0x23,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0xa,
            "msg_string": "That's easier said than done... But I guess I shouldn't doubt myself before trying."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x2,
            "name_id": 0x2,
            "extra_id": 0x1,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0xb,
            "msg_string": "You worked hard to make preparations too, after all."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x2,
            "name_id": 0x2,
            "extra_id": 0x3,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0xc,
            "msg_string": "Anyway, I'll go talk to Mr. Horst now. I'm sure I'll need to practice first."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x2,
            "name_id": 0x2,
            "extra_id": 0x3,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0xd,
            "msg_string": "...Sophie, we've come this far. Make sure you come watch."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x3e,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0xe,
            "msg_string": "Yeah, I'll definitely go."
        }
    ]
